column5: Where can I get Cuban Cigars in Vermilion Bay? Thanks, Tim
I used to get them at Bobby's on the west end of Vermillion Bay. Used to get cubans that were wrapped in silver foil and were 8 bucks apiece. Can't find them now.
Yep, Bobby's has them I found out. Thanks!
Do they have the cigars I was describing or does anyone know where I can get them?
>Can't afford them... cw Yah, that 8 bucks is 2 gallons of gas now! :-)
